---
title: Creamy Mushroom & Cherry Tomato Spaghetti with Parmesan & Garlic Pangrattato
description: You won’t believe the delicious end result of this pasta. Cream and stock infuse the spaghetti with beautiful sauciness and
flavour, leaving you with perfect strands of pasta covered in silky mushrooms and caramelised tomatoes.
